{"tid":143231,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣定馬來西亞?","createTime":"2017-03-04T12:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T16:34:28.000Z","uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55c48aba049517d4db0721aab3a3a3970488d776","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟現年19歲，以前因為一啲家庭原因<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋自己衰on9誤交損友</span></span>嘅原故，令到我嘅求學之路都唔係太順利，曾經輟學出o黎做野，又試過讀中專。轉折間最後都係決定起碼要完成個中學，因此入返去學校讀緊中五。<br />\n眼見身邊嘅朋友都已經grad哂，令我知道唔可以再浪費時間。而且香港嘅局勢變成咁，都令我產生移民嘅衝動。<br />\n問題就出現了，作為一個窮jj，我唔想再用屋企人錢，所以一定無可能一開始就去英美加澳等國留學。所以小弟諗出以下嘅解決方案:<br />\n<br />\n一.先到學費平嘅國家讀degree(如台灣\\馬來西亞),一路讀一路儲錢<br />\n二.攞完個degree後去其他國家讀一年制master(如加拿大)<br />\n三.讀完master搵工攞working visa，做夠一定時間申請移民<br />\n<br />\n雖然宜家好多窮jj最正路都會揀台灣，但係對比返馬來西亞，馬來西亞degree只需要讀三年，啱唒我呢啲唔想唒時間嘅人，而且當地大學全英語授課，對之後駁master或者improve自己嘅英文都有幫助。最重要嘅原因，就係佢地嘅生活模式同香港好唔同，可以見識下唔同嘅風土人情。<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴打會點揀，又或者有無其他更好嘅方案可以幫助我呢個迷茫嘅小毒男呢?"},{"pid":"1a3523fc0c043e1b5e670a9b2236fea7176b072f","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n想做IT狗，game develop<br />\n<br />\n暫時心水(台灣):<br />\n逢甲\\輔仁 <br />\n原因:同現校有聯繫，會比較易入;<br />\n台灣排名o黎講唔算差<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞:<br />\nAsia Pacific University of Technology &amp; Innovation<br />\nBSC (HONS) IN COMPUTER GAMES DEVELOPMENT<br />\n原因:<br />\n專攻it嘅大學，開正我個範"},{"pid":"a8815e351ed8e8cb4ceef87b2ecf55998267e829","tid":143231,"uid":25659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"比我會簡馬來西亞<br />\n去台灣d英文會退步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e657b369be8875e1c7aa8fac2bf9a628c9071e","tid":143231,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞啦<br />\n讀完書係個面創業都易啲<br />\n成本低好多"},{"pid":"11643d8938eeac05eb44bcfe8f149049adfbec06","tid":143231,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"Computer games..."},{"pid":"ffb3050fc87ddb02b9a70d05a8f7d69aba222c2e","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Computer games...</blockquote><br />\n恕小弟孤陋寡聞，Computer games有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學game engine嘅時候唔係都會接觸到其他平台嘅開發咩?真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b30f721bbc308d281b0c07c24725ae81c227c7","tid":143231,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？"},{"pid":"29e4735295563b75aebea49ccb6207f0011be607","tid":143231,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"馬來同台灣一樣都係全部學店<br />\n你不如反大陸暨南讀重好"},{"pid":"37113a9ce5dd3f432369fc5fe3122bb4ed72fb81","tid":143231,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬來同台灣一樣都係全部學店<br />\n你不如反大陸暨南讀重好</blockquote><br />\n你咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8993c9f90ac7d1a812b7ef907500b5f00731d29","tid":143231,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>馬來同台灣一樣都係全部學店<br />\n你不如反大陸暨南讀重好</blockquote><br />\n你咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想問咩"},{"pid":"80ae43cb5274bf11115b59826f79f65c166737e8","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬來同台灣一樣都係全部學店<br />\n你不如反大陸暨南讀重好</blockquote><br />\n寧願俾錢學店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3eee3a06f4b9af78b2fa3c65a218b453ecb4cb","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？</blockquote><br />\n其實逢甲同輔仁都唔算野雞嘅。至於馬來西亞，我都答你唔到，所以要上嚟問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea137ff0181643d7082fcfe848bcfcebb2a3a1c9","tid":143231,"uid":26399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？</blockquote><br />\n其實逢甲同輔仁都唔算野雞嘅。至於馬來西亞，我都答你唔到，所以要上嚟問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚唔驚呢兩間台大去到其他國家無認授性？到時巴打又晒左錢又晒左時間好唔抵"},{"pid":"6480eae417ab339dd10b5f0e61f53834f5fba172","tid":143231,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>馬來同台灣一樣都係全部學店<br />\n你不如反大陸暨南讀重好</blockquote><br />\n寧願俾錢學店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暨南狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3550a4284e2b07d236f65500c9d250f965393127","tid":143231,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:01:14.000Z","msg":"既然你都讀到中五 努力考埋個Dse 夠17 18分入台灣中字輩甚至台科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸升學你睇完個世界排名就知唔抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有 當你係台灣讀完學士 你會有半年時間搵公司請你 然後你必須係特定時間內得到台灣入息中位數一半以上嘅人工你就有機會移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b727f4b678de5caac3d67e46bc80e21cea615c21","tid":143231,"uid":72554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？</blockquote><br />\n中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4653c4dcc8714a6e9a68bd91ee9426af426d47a","tid":143231,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"乜撚技能都無學人講移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9025a5c5b51d30fd21a4cdf5cec97f2b8b76641","tid":143231,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"逢甲\\輔仁 <br />\n原因:同現校有聯繫，會比較易入;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣排名o黎講唔算差</span><br />\n<br />\n之後去加拿大讀 仲要拎埋working visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你拎台成交清都仲有可能<br />\n呢兩間你近乎0機會<br />\n根本冇工比你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢兩間係台灣黎講叫ok<br />\n但一出國 你都唔好講自己間大學出黎<br />\n負累黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9b6a108222da3fd8add22f1824a65322e47370","tid":143231,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？</blockquote><br />\n其實逢甲同輔仁都唔算野雞嘅。至於馬來西亞，我都答你唔到，所以要上嚟問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接d答你 你係當地人讀既話 唔差<br />\n<br />\n但如果係外地人都仲要讀呢d<br />\n係差到唔岩讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2611769f67d3a0c42bf7340ebeea6877cbfdfc3","tid":143231,"uid":63188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"逢甲夜市幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdb8fb9277e3d7cc6822e53082e93cac95d9326","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無知一問 其實個啲真係大學？</blockquote><br />\n其實逢甲同輔仁都唔算野雞嘅。至於馬來西亞，我都答你唔到，所以要上嚟問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接d答你 你係當地人讀既話 唔差<br />\n<br />\n但如果係外地人都仲要讀呢d<br />\n係差到唔岩讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9一問，拎上述兩間大學嘅degree駁唔駁到加拿大嘅master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7710ca8141ffe9bd813eab739ab6b0ada767ef3e","tid":143231,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚技能都無學人講移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未讀上去點會有技能？<br />\nbtw現時識寫c language,略懂Java script"},{"pid":"03e34e2a92e5619dd05bf05d4ce2a861b9e88aa6","tid":143231,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"馬拉經濟其實係咪好差<br />\n點解咁多人去第二到留學 都唔留係自己地方讀 最緊要佢d學生質素個個屈到仆街<br />\n香港就話父母望子成龍 廢西like me 入唔到香港大學先扔我出去"},{"pid":"47367a04df5f7e5ebe90e84786e560e1c7d55a28","tid":143231,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"馬拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同菲律賓大學一鳩樣"},{"pid":"fae29fdf148906089113474e5f26058d7cccc060","tid":143231,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同菲律賓大學一鳩樣</blockquote><br />\n一定係台灣，番香港master 機會大，但加拿大九成唔得"}]}